    "how_to_add_photos": [
      "1. Go to https://www.macaulaylibrary.org and search for the bird",
      "2. Pick a photo you like, note the asset number from the URL (e.g. 635230144)",
      "3. Build the URL: /bird-photos/FILENAME.jpg (save to public/bird-photos/)",
      "4. Add it to the photos array below with an appropriate label",
